Advent UCITS

















Advent UCITS Funds PLC 

Advent Capital Management, LLC (“Advent”), founded in 1995 by Tracy Maitland, is a SEC-registered investment advisor managing approximately $8.5 billion of client assets across alternative and traditional strategies (as of March 31, 2015). Advent is a fundamentally driven, research intensive asset manager with 20 year of experience investing and trading in global credit, equity and derivative markets. With offices in New York and London, Advent has a long tenured and highly skilled investment team supported by an institutional-quality risk management and operational infrastructure. Advent is solution-oriented and uniquely positioned to offer a suite of investment solutions with attractive risk/reward profiles.
Advent UCITS Funds plc (“Advent UCITS”) is an umbrella fund established as an open-ended investment company with variable capital incorporated with limited liability under the laws of Ireland. It qualifies and is authorised by the Central Bank of Ireland as an undertaking for collective investment in transferable securities (UCITS). Advent is the investment manager and promoter of Advent UCITS. Advent Capital Management UK Limited, which is authorised and regulated by the UK Financial Conduct Authority, is the distributor of Advent UCITS.
